# Flat apt repos to mirror with scripts/mirror-flat-repo.sh (run from postmirror.sh each sync).
# These have NO dists/<suite>/<component> tree (sourced with a trailing " /"), which apt-mirror
# can't mirror reliably — so they go here instead of mirror.list. Copy to:
#     /opt/apt/manager/flat-repos.list
# Format (one per line):   <flat-repo-url>  [ | <space-separated arches> ]
# Default arches if omitted: "amd64 all".  '#' starts a comment.
#
# Kubernetes is per-minor-version — add a line per version you support:
# https://pkgs.k8s.io/core:/stable:/v1.31/deb/ | amd64 all
# https://pkgs.k8s.io/core:/stable:/v1.30/deb/ | amd64 all
